room_title: Escape room "Zombie Outbreak: The Infection" by Encryption in Maryville
room_description: The zombie virus is quickly spreading and the government is frantically trying to get it under control. You and your team of 'volunteers' have unwittingly been duped to be test subjects in a research lab. You quickly learn that you've been infected, and the cure lies locked in a lab. Can you get the cure and get back out in time?
